# Docker Commands for Flutter Testing Calculator

```bash
cd testing
```

```bash
flutter clean
```

```bash
flutter pub get
```

```bash
flutter test
```

```bash
flutter build web
```

```bash
docker build -t testing-calculator .
```

```bash
docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name testing-calculator-container testing-calculator
```

```bash
docker stop testing-calculator-container
```

```bash
docker rm testing-calculator-container
```

```bash
flutter test
flutter build web
docker stop testing-calculator-container
docker rm testing-calculator-container
docker build -t testing-calculator .
docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name testing-calculator-container testing-calculator
```
